topic.title: Gentoo Linux - the highly flexible, source-based Linux distribution.
topic.body:
Lets talk everything Gentoo here :-)

What do you use Gentoo for?

Unsorted list of what I use it for
* Apache
* XMPP
* SMTP
* IMAP
* MariaDB
* Gnome
* Git
* NAS
* Btrfs - the best FS out there ;)
* Nextcloud
* Home router - WiFi, DHCP, FireWall, Router
